\subsection{Streaming Media}
Once the development environment was created the next task tackled was experimenting with different techniques of streaming media.\\
These techniques included:
\begin{itemize}
\item HTML5 Audio tag.
\item Spark Streaming.
\item Icecast.
\item SHOUTcast.
\item Darkice.
\item ezstream.
\item jPlayer.
\end{itemize}
Both HTML5 Audio tags and Spark Streaming were ruled out 